<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Blood Donation Confirmation</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #222222;
      }

      a {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .status {
        color: #fff;
        width: 100px;
        padding: 10px;
        animation: blink 2s infinite;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      @keyframes blink {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
        }

        to {
          opacity: 1;
        }
      }

      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .divider {
        border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #1e1e1e;
        padding: 30px;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 14px;
        background-color: #f4f3f3;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #1e1e1e;
        padding: 14px;
        color: #ef5b5b;
      }

      img {
        padding: 24px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dap91fhxh/image/upload/v1720958373/logo1_ewwjxg.png"
          height="100px"
          width="400px"
          alt="BloodBridge Logo"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for your generous blood donation.</p>
        <p>Here are your details:</p>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= name %></p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
        <p><strong>Tel:</strong> <%= tel %></p>
        <p><strong>Address:</strong> <%= address %></p>
        <p><strong>Blood Group:</strong> <%= bloodgroup %></p>
        <p><strong>Any Disease in Blood:</strong> <%= diseases %></p>
        <p><strong>Weight:</strong> <%= weight %> kg</p>
        <p><strong>Blood Pressure:</strong> <%= bloodpressure %></p>
        <p><strong>Age:</strong> <%= age %> years</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= date %></p>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>Here are the details of places you can donate blood:</p>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> Red Cross Blood Donation Center</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> July 20, 2024</p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> 10:00 AM</p>
        <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Main Street, Cityville</p>
        <p>Contact Numbers:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>(123) 456-7890</li>
          <li>(234) 567-8901</li>
          <li>(345) 678-9012</li>
          <li>(456) 789-0123</li>
          <li>(567) 890-1234</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> Community Health Center</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> July 22, 2024</p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> 2:00 PM</p>
        <p><strong>Address:</strong> 456 Elm Street, Townsville</p>
        <p>Contact Numbers:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>(678) 901-2345</li>
          <li>(789) 012-3456</li>
          <li>(890) 123-4567</li>
          <li>(901) 234-5678</li>
          <li>(012) 345-6789</li>
        </ul>
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dap91fhxh/image/upload/v1720957791/hero1_trpojy.jpg"
          alt="Blood Donation"
          height="250px"
          width="500px"
        />
        <h3>Note:</h3>
        <p>If you did not apply for blood donation, please contact us immediately.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>
          If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at
          <a href="mailto:support@bloodbridge.com">support@bloodbridge.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
